flowchart TB
  Start[UIUX task] --> Ground{P0 Grounding}
  Ground -->|found| Explore[P1 Explore directions]
  Ground -->|none| Stop[Ask human]
  Explore --> Pick{P2 Pick direction}
  Pick --> Lock[Write style lock]
  Lock --> Build[P3 Build]
  Build --> Unify{P4 Unify checks}
  Unify -->|fail| Build
  Unify -->|pass| Review{P5 Review loop}
  Review -->|fail| Unify
  Review -->|pass| Gate[uiux gate.ship]
